WEBVTT

01:37.830 --> 01:40.590
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.330 --> 01:43.700
[Episode 10]

01:50.150 --> 01:50.710
Mr. Lu,

01:50.880 --> 01:51.940
where are we going?

01:53.070 --> 01:53.759
Qiyue Lake.

01:54.620 --> 01:55.880
The water of Qiyue Lake

01:56.000 --> 01:57.000
in Chongling Valley is clear

01:57.000 --> 01:58.200
with rich spiritual energy.

01:58.200 --> 01:59.400
It is extraordinary.

01:59.789 --> 02:00.590
The spiritual plants here

02:00.590 --> 02:01.850
are also growing well.

02:01.920 --> 02:04.180
They're all nourished by the lake water.

02:04.840 --> 02:05.840
That explains why

02:05.840 --> 02:08.500
the trees here
are growing exceptionally well.

02:39.530 --> 02:40.470
I slipped Power-Dissolving Powder

02:40.470 --> 02:41.400
into your tea

02:42.030 --> 02:43.360
to suppress your power.

02:43.590 --> 02:45.720
You are no different from a mortal now.

02:45.910 --> 02:47.640
You won't be able to break free.

02:54.360 --> 02:55.960
I'll ask, and you'll answer.

02:56.350 --> 02:57.280
Will you do that?

03:04.960 --> 03:06.030
This is my senior,

03:06.630 --> 03:08.870
She left the mountain for errands
and hasn't returned for a long time.

03:08.870 --> 03:09.710
You know her,

03:10.280 --> 03:10.880
don't you?

03:12.000 --> 03:12.870
So what if I do?

03:13.430 --> 03:15.400
There's a grudge between you and her.

03:15.400 --> 03:16.660
You're an enemy to her.

03:20.240 --> 03:21.300
One last question.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.630
Was the female cultivator trying to avenge

03:23.630 --> 03:25.079
her husband in the capital

03:25.079 --> 03:26.030
my senior?

03:27.360 --> 03:28.890
Were you chasing after her?

03:29.150 --> 03:30.079
Did she get hurt?

03:30.430 --> 03:31.490
I really am curious

03:32.090 --> 03:33.530
about what kind of sect

03:33.560 --> 03:34.870
could raise two ignorant fools

03:34.870 --> 03:36.670
courting death like you and her.

03:36.860 --> 03:38.000
She deserves death for violating

03:38.000 --> 03:39.800
the rules set for immortal sects.

03:39.800 --> 03:41.280
You want to stand up for her now?

03:41.280 --> 03:42.880
Who do you think you are to...

03:46.750 --> 03:48.010
Write down everything

03:48.240 --> 03:48.970
you've heard

03:49.440 --> 03:51.090
and seen

03:51.120 --> 03:52.050
about my senior.

03:55.030 --> 03:57.079
You think I'll do that
just because you tell me to?

03:57.079 --> 03:58.050
Today, I was captured by you

03:58.050 --> 03:59.710
simply because I had bad luck.

03:59.870 --> 04:01.330
But what about the future?

04:01.800 --> 04:02.710
I am backed

04:02.710 --> 04:03.910
by Lingji Mountain.

04:04.590 --> 04:05.790
Do you dare to kill me?

04:17.950 --> 04:18.600
My senior

04:18.620 --> 04:20.620
prayed for me and got me this amulet.

04:20.630 --> 04:22.490
She said I had a bitter childhood,

04:22.800 --> 04:24.680
but living with her from then on

04:25.310 --> 04:27.110
would be equal to having family.

04:27.160 --> 04:28.600
She wished me all the best in everything,

04:28.600 --> 04:30.130
and peace and joy in my life.

04:30.950 --> 04:32.000
However, in fact,

04:32.720 --> 04:33.830
I do have family.

04:34.720 --> 04:36.320
My mother passed away early.

04:36.870 --> 04:38.870
My father has many children,

04:39.510 --> 04:40.710
all of which are boys,

04:41.240 --> 04:42.390
except me.

04:44.000 --> 04:44.830
Do you know

04:45.680 --> 04:46.870
how I survived

04:47.310 --> 04:48.630
in a family like that?

04:50.310 --> 04:52.390
I had to grovel all day long

04:53.120 --> 04:54.870
and wait on them like a slave.

04:55.830 --> 04:57.390
Whenever they felt displeased,

04:57.390 --> 04:59.360
they would punch and kick me.

05:00.950 --> 05:02.880
Occasionally, I fell into a trance

05:03.290 --> 05:04.090
and wondered

05:04.120 --> 05:05.980
if I was a living soul in this world

05:06.800 --> 05:08.600
or if I had already entered hell.

05:10.240 --> 05:11.570
What are you going to do?

05:14.190 --> 05:15.480
But on second thought,

05:16.560 --> 05:17.480
I assumed...

05:18.800 --> 05:20.860
even hell couldn't be that terrible.

05:21.390 --> 05:22.190
Later,

05:22.660 --> 05:24.250
it took me a great deal of effort

05:24.250 --> 05:25.280
to escape

05:25.310 --> 05:26.370
from that inferno.

05:27.120 --> 05:28.720
If my senior hadn't saved me,

05:29.190 --> 05:30.450
brought me to the sect,

05:31.390 --> 05:32.680
taken good care of me,

05:33.120 --> 05:34.580
and taught me techniques,

05:34.920 --> 05:36.380
I would have died long ago.

05:37.600 --> 05:39.120
To me, my senior matters

05:39.600 --> 05:41.600
more than anyone else in this world.

05:42.720 --> 05:44.920
She's even more important than my life.

05:50.070 --> 05:51.070
Stay away from me.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.430
What on earth are you going to do?

06:04.720 --> 06:05.680
You're crazy!

06:13.920 --> 06:14.600
Given that,

06:15.480 --> 06:17.210
I guess you understand how much

06:17.830 --> 06:19.720
I want to kill you right now.

06:31.920 --> 06:32.380
What...

06:33.270 --> 06:34.130
What did you...

06:34.190 --> 06:35.000
do to me?

06:37.430 --> 06:39.120
I cast the Bonding Curse on you.

06:39.120 --> 06:40.580
The cursed ones will share

06:40.750 --> 06:42.280
the same fate and feelings.

06:42.560 --> 06:43.870
I do want to kill you.

06:44.390 --> 06:46.650
But my senior told me
to be kind to others,

06:46.930 --> 06:48.270
and to avoid staining my hands with blood

06:48.270 --> 06:49.930
because of others' mistakes.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.930
I choose to listen to her

06:52.630 --> 06:53.760
and spare your life.

07:15.240 --> 07:15.920
Now,

07:16.950 --> 07:18.280
will you tell the truth?

07:40.560 --> 07:41.070
I already told you

07:41.070 --> 07:42.400
what you wanted to know.

07:42.630 --> 07:43.890
When will you let me go?

07:46.830 --> 07:48.950
You're better at reading the situation
than she is,

07:48.950 --> 07:50.280
but not as honest as her.

07:55.000 --> 07:55.510
Look.

07:56.480 --> 07:57.240
She wrote

07:57.870 --> 07:59.720
much content than you did.

08:00.720 --> 08:01.800
You only asked if I knew

08:01.800 --> 08:03.130
where your senior went.

08:04.390 --> 08:05.850
My answer was impeccable.

08:06.120 --> 08:07.070
But you didn't tell me

08:07.070 --> 08:08.390
she was with an extraordinary fighter

08:08.390 --> 08:09.840
who helped her out of trouble.

08:09.840 --> 08:11.240
You've seen that fighter.

08:11.240 --> 08:12.170
What is his name?

08:12.630 --> 08:13.890
What does he look like?

08:13.950 --> 08:14.750
Draw his face.

08:14.950 --> 08:16.190
I only got a glimpse of him.

08:16.190 --> 08:17.480
I can't remember his face clearly.

08:17.480 --> 08:18.810
Even if I remembered it,

08:19.630 --> 08:21.230
I wouldn't be able to draw it.

08:22.830 --> 08:23.720
It's fine.

08:24.870 --> 08:26.270
The night is still young.

08:26.720 --> 08:28.380
There is plenty of time for us.

09:17.910 --> 09:18.970
Forgive me, ma'am.

09:19.180 --> 09:20.420
I was thirsty from the journey,

09:20.420 --> 09:22.080
so I poured myself a cup of tea.

09:22.150 --> 09:23.750
I will pay whatever it costs.

09:23.840 --> 09:25.300
It's just a cup of cold tea.

09:25.390 --> 09:26.790
Consider it on the house.

09:33.550 --> 09:34.910
You've finished your tea.

09:34.910 --> 09:36.080
Why are you still here?

09:36.080 --> 09:38.140
Two of my friends are being kept here.

09:38.240 --> 09:39.750
I'm afraid I won't leave

09:41.030 --> 09:42.360
until you release them.

09:50.840 --> 09:53.040
You really are haunting me like a ghost.

09:56.720 --> 09:58.250
Please release them, miss.

09:59.480 --> 10:01.440
You're asking for trouble.

11:35.150 --> 11:37.120
We are both Golden Core cultivators.

11:37.120 --> 11:38.270
Even if we keep fighting,

11:38.270 --> 11:39.840
there's no telling who will win.

11:39.840 --> 11:40.840
Let my friends go.

11:41.200 --> 11:42.720
I don't want to give you a hard time.

11:42.720 --> 11:44.200
You colluded with them

11:44.390 --> 11:45.720
to try to kill my senior.

11:45.910 --> 11:47.770
How is it not giving me a hard time?

12:05.150 --> 12:05.810
Senior Jin,

12:06.000 --> 12:06.840
let me help you.

12:06.840 --> 12:07.550
Forget about me.

12:07.550 --> 12:08.810
Go find Nangong first!

12:10.510 --> 12:11.550
You must memorize

12:11.870 --> 12:12.840
every single word

12:12.840 --> 12:14.170
of what I'm going to say.

12:15.200 --> 12:16.720
Humans are connected
to the external environment.

12:16.720 --> 12:17.910
They exhale the impure
and inhale the fresh

12:17.910 --> 12:19.440
through the nose and mouth.

12:19.870 --> 12:21.530
Cultivators' focus is more on

12:21.720 --> 12:24.180
improving the complete sensory faculties.

12:24.370 --> 12:25.240
Only when a cultivator

12:25.240 --> 12:27.480
senses things that ordinary people can't

12:27.480 --> 12:29.720
will his or her body form a link
with heaven and earth,

12:29.720 --> 12:31.180
take in spiritual energy,

12:31.390 --> 12:32.720
and go to a higher stage.

12:33.720 --> 12:35.080
Mr. Lu, if, as you said,

12:35.550 --> 12:37.670
one can breathe
without using the mouth or nose,

12:37.670 --> 12:39.670
does it mean I can take in water
the same way?

12:39.670 --> 12:40.470
Yes, exactly.

12:41.200 --> 12:42.210
I'm going to teach you

12:42.210 --> 12:43.870
the Fish Drinking Technique.

12:44.320 --> 12:45.650
It means to take in water

12:45.790 --> 12:46.840
like fish do.

12:47.320 --> 12:49.000
Hold your breath and gather your energy.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.330
Let your mind settle at Lingtai acupoint.

12:57.720 --> 12:58.960
Have your energy flow through your body

12:58.960 --> 13:00.180
and reach Hegu acupoint.

13:00.180 --> 13:01.580
Close the heart meridians.

13:01.580 --> 13:03.580
Let your spiritual energy run along

13:04.080 --> 13:06.670
all the meridians
and gather on the skin.

13:23.120 --> 13:25.450
I can feel my vital energy
is circulating.

13:25.960 --> 13:27.160
May I drink water now?

13:27.870 --> 13:28.730
Not in a moment.

13:36.120 --> 13:36.520
Mr. Lu!

13:39.030 --> 13:39.550
Mr. Lu!

13:40.200 --> 13:40.930
Don't panic.

13:40.960 --> 13:42.840
Breathe with the technique I taught you.

13:42.840 --> 13:43.770
You've got this.

13:50.840 --> 13:51.240
No.

14:32.450 --> 14:33.600
The Power-Dissolving Powder

14:33.600 --> 14:35.080
has stopped you from using techniques.

14:35.080 --> 14:37.480
But I didn't expect
you could still resort to sword skills.

14:37.480 --> 14:38.740
I underestimated you.

14:39.200 --> 14:41.240
We'll remember what you did to us today

14:41.240 --> 14:43.300
and make you pay a steep price one day.

15:12.830 --> 15:15.160
She used Power-Dissolving Powder on you?

15:16.630 --> 15:17.430
Not only that.

15:18.080 --> 15:20.080
She also cast the Bonding Curse on me

15:20.360 --> 15:22.220
and tortured me with a little bug,

15:22.510 --> 15:24.770
which almost made me suffocate to death.

15:25.270 --> 15:26.750
Why did she catch the two of you?

15:26.750 --> 15:28.120
What else reason could it be?

15:28.120 --> 15:29.380
Her senior, of course.

15:29.720 --> 15:30.550
The female cultivator

15:30.550 --> 15:33.210
who took revenge for her husband
in the capital.

15:35.030 --> 15:36.790
Forget about this matter then.

15:37.240 --> 15:38.750
Go back to your sects for recuperation.

15:38.750 --> 15:39.810
I will go after her.

15:40.080 --> 15:40.940
Thank you then.

15:42.030 --> 15:42.690
Senior Jin,

15:44.120 --> 15:45.720
you must not let her get away.

15:50.080 --> 15:51.080
Rub your hair dry.

15:54.790 --> 15:56.910
I'll take you to practice more
these few days.

15:56.910 --> 15:59.840
It's not hard to master
the Fish Drinking Technique.

16:00.840 --> 16:01.510
Mr. Lu,

16:02.000 --> 16:02.630
tell me,

16:03.120 --> 16:05.240
after getting the hang
of the Fish Drinking Technique,

16:05.240 --> 16:07.240
will I no longer need to drink water?

16:08.270 --> 16:09.910
Are you thirsty now?

16:11.240 --> 16:12.440
No, I don't think I am.

16:13.510 --> 16:15.040
I'm really not thirsty now.

16:15.600 --> 16:17.390
Thank you for saving my life, Mr. Lu.

16:17.390 --> 16:19.120
I will never forget your favor.

16:19.480 --> 16:20.680
If you ever need help,

16:20.720 --> 16:21.670
I'll come to your aid

16:21.670 --> 16:22.800
despite any danger.

16:24.030 --> 16:26.150
I don't need you to go through any danger.

16:26.150 --> 16:27.720
It'll save me a lot of trouble
if you could

16:27.720 --> 16:29.480
master the Fish Drinking Technique soon.

16:29.480 --> 16:30.480
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

16:39.670 --> 16:40.800
Hungry, aren't you?

16:41.600 --> 16:43.030
I haven't eaten anything for a whole day.

16:43.030 --> 16:43.830
But it's fine.

16:44.240 --> 16:46.080
I'll find something to eat later.

16:46.080 --> 16:47.610
Given your current health,

16:47.750 --> 16:48.680
what can you eat?

16:51.600 --> 16:52.740
Flatbreads.

16:53.390 --> 16:54.320
Dry flatbreads.

16:56.240 --> 16:56.790
Got it.

16:57.790 --> 16:58.450
Wait for me.

18:24.400 --> 18:25.070
Mr. Lu.

18:26.880 --> 18:27.610
Here you are.

18:27.920 --> 18:28.400
Dig in.

18:29.790 --> 18:30.650
Thanks, Mr. Lu.

18:38.000 --> 18:38.930
Anything wrong?

18:39.350 --> 18:39.920
Nothing.

18:40.830 --> 18:41.640
Mr. Lu,

18:42.110 --> 18:43.880
did you make this yourself?

18:45.000 --> 18:45.400
Yes.

18:53.750 --> 18:55.590
Does it taste awful?

18:55.960 --> 18:56.590
Not at all.

18:57.200 --> 18:57.860
It's tasty.

19:00.020 --> 19:01.150
A bit salty, though.

19:02.800 --> 19:03.590
I'll cook again then.

19:03.590 --> 19:04.250
No, No need.

19:04.880 --> 19:06.210
I'd hate to waste these.

19:11.160 --> 19:11.690
Alright.

19:11.750 --> 19:12.880
It's good to eat now.

19:19.720 --> 19:20.580
How delicious.

19:25.400 --> 19:26.060
Spit it out.

19:26.790 --> 19:27.960
Or it'll upset your stomach.

19:27.960 --> 19:28.960
That won't be a problem.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.360
It actually tastes good.

19:31.790 --> 19:33.120
Had better not waste it.

19:37.000 --> 19:37.480
Yummy.

19:42.790 --> 19:43.480
Mr. Lu,

19:44.390 --> 19:45.450
actually, it would

19:45.590 --> 19:48.350
be better if you had made these flatbreads

19:48.880 --> 19:49.480
thinner.

19:50.070 --> 19:52.200
This way, they would be easier to cook.

19:52.550 --> 19:53.590
You know how to make flatbreads?

19:53.590 --> 19:54.390
Yes, a little.

19:55.880 --> 19:57.510
How thin should they be?

19:59.750 --> 20:01.440
About half as thin as this one.

20:02.510 --> 20:03.590
When you mix the flour with water,

20:03.590 --> 20:04.520
put in some salt.

20:05.160 --> 20:05.960
Not a handful,

20:06.200 --> 20:07.060
but a spoonful.

20:08.510 --> 20:09.370
Anything else?

20:09.830 --> 20:11.110
When you knead the dough,

20:11.110 --> 20:12.200
try adding an egg

20:12.510 --> 20:14.650
and sprinkling some chopped green onions.

20:14.650 --> 20:15.720
Then, when the flatbreads are ready,

20:15.720 --> 20:16.830
they'll smell better

20:16.830 --> 20:18.090
with a crispy texture.

20:18.510 --> 20:19.550
If there's a chance in the future,

20:19.550 --> 20:20.880
let me make some for you.

20:22.920 --> 20:23.440
Yes.

20:24.810 --> 20:27.710
[Mingzhu House]

20:37.440 --> 20:38.240
Let's team up.

20:39.310 --> 20:40.370
Young Sect Master,

20:40.480 --> 20:41.200
Are we going

20:41.550 --> 20:42.350
to steal, rob,

20:43.030 --> 20:43.880
or purchase?

20:46.180 --> 20:47.380
Haven't decided yet.

20:51.760 --> 20:52.820
Young Sect Master,

20:52.970 --> 20:53.900
there's a thief.

21:14.480 --> 21:16.140
What exquisite sword skills.

21:16.230 --> 21:17.960
You even made me use magic techniques.

21:17.960 --> 21:18.790
Impressive.

21:28.240 --> 21:29.070
Young Sect Master,

21:29.070 --> 21:30.000
are you alright?

21:57.910 --> 21:59.310
Are you done practicing?

22:00.030 --> 22:01.090
Such long practice

22:01.400 --> 22:02.260
has worn me out.

22:08.720 --> 22:09.960
Food is ready in Cunsu Hall.

22:09.960 --> 22:10.690
Let's go eat!

22:12.070 --> 22:12.670
Fine then.

22:19.640 --> 22:20.590
It's been so long.

22:20.590 --> 22:21.990
Why isn't it our turn yet?

22:22.240 --> 22:23.480
We've waited for a long time.

22:23.480 --> 22:25.030
My mother is in agony.

22:25.270 --> 22:26.790
When will we be allowed in?

22:28.000 --> 22:28.720
Tell me about it.

22:28.720 --> 22:30.320
What's taking so long today?

22:32.880 --> 22:33.940
Next is the patient

22:34.030 --> 22:35.100
with the call sign "Geng."

22:35.100 --> 22:36.030
Yes, here we are!

22:36.440 --> 22:38.300
Young Sect Master, it's our turn.

22:39.640 --> 22:40.970
I've been in line for so long.

22:40.970 --> 22:41.590
When will it

22:41.590 --> 22:42.640
be our turn?

22:50.070 --> 22:51.270
This external injury

22:51.480 --> 22:53.160
of your could be fixed

22:53.160 --> 22:54.270
in any other clinic.

22:54.270 --> 22:56.920
Why did you have to wait in line
with my other patients?

22:56.920 --> 22:58.520
Your wound is almost healed.

23:03.310 --> 23:04.770
B-But aren't you said to be

23:04.880 --> 23:06.010
the best physician?

23:06.350 --> 23:07.720
My master even better.

23:08.000 --> 23:09.310
Why don't you go to him?

23:09.790 --> 23:11.160
Only if I could find him!

23:12.960 --> 23:13.350
Wait.

23:14.160 --> 23:15.620
Just treat your patients.

23:16.030 --> 23:17.090
What is it with you?

23:22.480 --> 23:23.810
How did you get injured?

23:24.750 --> 23:27.410
Someone set off firecrackers
when I was around.

23:27.680 --> 23:28.610
I don't think so.

23:29.310 --> 23:30.680
It was probably gunpowder.

23:30.680 --> 23:32.510
The Human Race's craftsmanship
develops rapidly.

23:32.510 --> 23:34.240
They invented gunpowder long ago.

23:34.240 --> 23:36.000
It can be as powerful as magic.

23:36.640 --> 23:38.960
Goddess Wushuang once wrote a book

23:39.400 --> 23:40.720
called "Unparalleled Secret Magic,"

23:40.720 --> 23:43.180
which records many mysterious techniques.

23:43.640 --> 23:46.030
Unfortunately, this book
has been long lost.

23:46.030 --> 23:46.880
Otherwise,

23:47.160 --> 23:49.800
the Human Race would be much better
than now.

23:51.070 --> 23:52.400
This is news to me.

23:53.240 --> 23:54.400
So you're saying

23:54.790 --> 23:56.000
that with gunpowder,

23:56.310 --> 23:58.640
even little kids can fend for themselves?

24:03.680 --> 24:04.920
Having said all that,

24:05.590 --> 24:07.550
Chongling Valley acquiesces

24:08.030 --> 24:08.790
in letting someone use

24:08.790 --> 24:10.550
such a dangerous thing at night.

24:10.550 --> 24:11.640
Won't you do something?

24:11.640 --> 24:13.370
Aren't you partially to blame?

24:15.030 --> 24:16.360
Then what were you doing

24:16.720 --> 24:17.680
so late at night?

24:18.880 --> 24:20.830
Why did you get in a fight with someone?

24:20.830 --> 24:21.200
I...

24:27.030 --> 24:28.030
What a huge wound.

24:29.310 --> 24:30.240
Young Sect Master,

24:30.240 --> 24:32.310
how much of this medicine
should be taken a day?

24:32.310 --> 24:33.530
I can't read Physician Zhu Yu's

24:33.530 --> 24:34.680
handwriting at all.

24:35.350 --> 24:36.880
To hell with that medicine.

24:37.200 --> 24:39.110
I can't believe he gave me such trash.

24:39.110 --> 24:40.000
Chongling Valley

24:40.000 --> 24:41.660
has become so disrespectful.

24:43.590 --> 24:44.920
Give me a Yangyuan Pill.

25:02.590 --> 25:03.680
Isn't that Immortal Xin

25:03.680 --> 25:04.740
from Xin Xie Manor?

25:05.590 --> 25:06.990
Who is the man beside her?

25:08.750 --> 25:10.440
He's no ordinary man.

25:25.110 --> 25:25.790
Miss Xin!

25:32.070 --> 25:33.790
Does the food here agree with you?

25:33.790 --> 25:35.270
Yes, every bit as good
as that in Zuixian Restaurant.

25:35.270 --> 25:36.270
The taste is excellent,

25:36.270 --> 25:36.670
and...

25:38.750 --> 25:40.210
we don't have to pay at all.

25:41.720 --> 25:42.520
Your friends?

25:43.590 --> 25:44.380
Please meet

25:44.630 --> 25:45.760
Miss Lyu Yunsu.

25:45.790 --> 25:46.350
She is

25:46.790 --> 25:48.510
the daughter of General Lyu Jing.

25:48.510 --> 25:49.400
This is Li Si,

25:49.680 --> 25:51.000
captain of the Dongyou Army.

25:51.000 --> 25:51.960
This is Mr. Lu,

25:52.270 --> 25:54.000
a friend of Divine Doctor Su's.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.540
Greetings, Mr. Su.

25:58.140 --> 26:00.670
Zuixian Restaurant has no branches
in the capital.

26:00.670 --> 26:01.900
The Dongyou Army is stationed

26:01.900 --> 26:04.100
a thousand miles away from the capital.

26:04.110 --> 26:05.970
Have you been to that restaurant?

26:07.440 --> 26:08.030
Never.

26:08.720 --> 26:09.520
Well, you see,

26:10.070 --> 26:11.470
we are from a small place.

26:11.770 --> 26:12.880
We've only heard of the well reputed

26:12.880 --> 26:14.070
Zuixian Restaurant.

26:14.070 --> 26:15.550
So when we eat something nice,

26:15.550 --> 26:17.550
we can't help but make a comparison.

26:18.200 --> 26:20.260
I must've humiliated myself, Mr. Lu.

26:20.270 --> 26:22.130
But your comparison was on point.

26:22.160 --> 26:23.510
The master chef of Cunsu Hall

26:23.510 --> 26:24.240
used to truly

26:24.270 --> 26:25.830
work in Zuixian Restaurant.

26:25.830 --> 26:27.240
So many years have passed.

26:27.240 --> 26:28.480
The current chef there

26:28.480 --> 26:30.080
is probably his apprentice.

26:32.200 --> 26:33.130
Nice to meet you.

26:37.510 --> 26:38.570
You mean together?

26:38.640 --> 26:39.110
Please.

26:39.960 --> 26:41.090
Thank you, Miss Lyu.

26:41.350 --> 26:42.640
Shall we join them?

26:43.960 --> 26:44.510
Sure.

26:52.400 --> 26:53.860
What would you like to eat?

26:54.720 --> 26:55.200
Thanks.

26:55.680 --> 26:56.590
A plate of flatbreads,

26:56.590 --> 26:57.480
and a pot of wine.

26:57.480 --> 26:57.880
Got it!

26:58.280 --> 26:59.270
Just a moment, sir.

26:59.270 --> 27:00.020
Mr. Lu,

27:00.240 --> 27:01.570
won't you eat anything?

27:01.830 --> 27:02.830
Wine is all I need.

27:03.680 --> 27:04.480
There is some.

27:13.070 --> 27:13.590
Mr. Lu.

27:17.950 --> 27:18.780
Is the Dongyou Army's

27:18.780 --> 27:20.040
Left General Sun Wulei

27:20.480 --> 27:21.240
still unable

27:21.640 --> 27:22.900
to hold his liquor now?

27:24.720 --> 27:26.450
The Left General never drinks,

27:26.550 --> 27:28.150
and his name is not Sun Wulei.

27:28.680 --> 27:30.080
He is General Zhang Qian.

27:31.960 --> 27:33.510
Captain Li, judging by your hand,

27:33.510 --> 27:35.310
you don't seem to be a sword user.

27:36.240 --> 27:37.790
I'm better at using short-bladed weapons.

27:37.790 --> 27:39.190
But occasionally, I use swords as well.

27:39.190 --> 27:40.790
A military man using swords?

27:41.140 --> 27:42.480
How do you kill enemies then?

27:42.480 --> 27:44.030
I used to be a scout,
with the primary duty

27:44.030 --> 27:45.690
of reconnoitering the enemy.

27:45.750 --> 27:47.200
Only when I was discovered

27:47.200 --> 27:48.070
or besieged would I really

27:48.070 --> 27:49.400
need to fight the enemy.

27:49.480 --> 27:51.140
In a life-or-death situation,

27:51.140 --> 27:53.340
a sword or a dagger makes no difference.

27:58.830 --> 28:02.310
Mr. Lu, have you served
in the army as well?

28:02.620 --> 28:03.460
She's asking...

28:03.460 --> 28:04.390
Yes, for a while.

28:07.260 --> 28:09.320
So you can read sign language, Mr. Lu?

28:10.480 --> 28:11.080
Yes, a bit.

28:14.200 --> 28:15.000
Please enjoy.

28:15.400 --> 28:16.110
Dig in.

28:21.720 --> 28:23.070
I am Lin Muhan from Lingji Mountain.

28:23.070 --> 28:25.110
Such a pleasure to meet you,
a junior from Xin Xie Manor.

28:25.110 --> 28:26.690
I... I don't know you.

28:28.110 --> 28:30.000
Lingji Mountain and Xin Xie Manor

28:30.030 --> 28:31.360
have always been close.

28:31.440 --> 28:33.000
My father and your master, Xin Xiong,

28:33.000 --> 28:34.060
are bosom friends.

28:34.680 --> 28:36.210
I heard your birthday is...

28:36.480 --> 28:38.240
the ninth day of the ninth lunar month.

28:38.240 --> 28:40.200
So you're the Heavenly Talent
of Xin Xie Manor.

28:40.200 --> 28:40.960
What a coincidence.

28:40.960 --> 28:42.390
I am also a Heavenly Talent too.

28:42.390 --> 28:44.480
That makes this
a meeting of Heavenly Talents.

28:44.480 --> 28:45.480
I wish we could

28:45.500 --> 28:46.470
meet earlier.

28:47.880 --> 28:48.740
Hello, Mr. Lin.

28:51.310 --> 28:52.510
This gentleman...

28:53.790 --> 28:55.000
looks very familiar.

28:55.920 --> 28:57.580
Have we met somewhere before?

28:59.350 --> 29:00.210
I remember now.

29:00.750 --> 29:02.550
We once met at the Safe Haven Inn.

29:02.880 --> 29:03.720
Sir, you were having

29:03.720 --> 29:05.680
a good time chatting with the pharmacists

29:05.680 --> 29:07.010
from Chongling Valley.

29:07.030 --> 29:08.630
I meant to go up and greet you,

29:09.000 --> 29:09.860
but it was a pity

29:10.030 --> 29:11.960
you and your fellows left too soon.

29:12.960 --> 29:13.760
But it's fine.

29:14.160 --> 29:15.830
It was fate that brought us
together again.

29:15.830 --> 29:16.310
Sir,

29:16.880 --> 29:18.010
why not be my friend?

29:26.000 --> 29:28.200
Sir, you're drinking without talking.

29:29.070 --> 29:30.400
That's not respectful.

29:31.000 --> 29:33.530
I'll take it that you don't want me
as a friend.

29:33.750 --> 29:35.750
Mr. Lin, please don't take offense.

29:35.790 --> 29:37.880
Aloofness is Mr. Lu's personal trait.

29:37.880 --> 29:38.720
He doesn't like to talk.

29:38.720 --> 29:41.050
Please don't give him a hard time,
Mr. Lin.

29:41.640 --> 29:42.840
You call him "Mr. Lu"?

30:04.920 --> 30:05.780
Sir, we'll have

30:05.880 --> 30:07.720
half a kilo of beef
and four bowls of plain noodles.

30:07.720 --> 30:08.240
Got it!

30:08.440 --> 30:10.040
Take a seat and wait a moment.

30:10.440 --> 30:10.960
There are new customers.

30:10.960 --> 30:11.550
Tell the kitchen

30:11.550 --> 30:14.950
to prepare half a kilo of beef
and four bowls of plain noodles.

30:19.030 --> 30:19.680
Sorry.

30:20.160 --> 30:21.220
This seat is taken.

30:24.510 --> 30:25.160
Hurry, go.

30:25.300 --> 30:26.150
Bai Zongying,

30:26.640 --> 30:29.300
how dare you hurt
a member of us Lingji Mountain?

30:29.570 --> 30:30.720
Let's go. Quick.

30:37.070 --> 30:38.160
Fine.

30:39.200 --> 30:40.930
Another man who wouldn't talk.

31:20.320 --> 31:21.480
I didn't realize you are such

31:21.480 --> 31:22.610
an amazing fighter.

31:23.510 --> 31:25.640
I really underestimated you that day.

31:26.790 --> 31:27.850
You enjoy the food.

31:28.070 --> 31:29.000
I'm leaving now.

31:31.780 --> 31:32.710
I'm leaving too.

32:02.830 --> 32:03.830
You know that man?

32:06.880 --> 32:08.680
About the one who came in later...

32:08.680 --> 32:09.920
Judging by his clothes,

32:09.920 --> 32:11.720
he's from Tianyuan Sect, right?

32:12.680 --> 32:14.110
He's the personal disciple of Li Mofu,

32:14.110 --> 32:16.070
namely the master of Tianyuan Sect.

32:16.070 --> 32:17.030
he has top-notch powers

32:17.030 --> 32:18.430
and superb sword skills.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.000
I do know him,

32:20.590 --> 32:22.450
but he might not remember who I am.

32:23.200 --> 32:23.590
Sir!

32:24.160 --> 32:25.290
Sir, please hold on!

32:26.310 --> 32:26.880
Sir,

32:27.550 --> 32:28.880
thank you for your help.

32:29.240 --> 32:30.070
Lingji Mountain

32:30.070 --> 32:31.920
will remember the favor you did me.

32:31.920 --> 32:32.400
Sir,

32:32.880 --> 32:33.970
if you ever need help

32:33.970 --> 32:34.860
in the future,

32:35.110 --> 32:36.030
don't hesitate

32:36.240 --> 32:37.440
to turn to us anytime.

32:37.720 --> 32:39.120
Honestly, destiny seems

32:39.400 --> 32:41.480
to have formed a connection between us.

32:41.480 --> 32:43.070
Which sect are you from?
Who is your master?

32:43.070 --> 32:45.200
Have you ever been to Lingji Mountain?

33:05.440 --> 33:06.160
Mr. Lu,

33:06.590 --> 33:08.240
would you like to come in and sit?

33:08.240 --> 33:09.770
Although I can't drink tea,

33:09.830 --> 33:11.230
I could make some for you.

33:11.920 --> 33:12.510
No need.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.060
Maybe another day.

33:26.750 --> 33:27.440
Mr. Lu!

33:36.830 --> 33:38.090
My room was ransacked.

33:48.010 --> 33:49.590
Mom, I want candied hawthorns.

33:49.590 --> 33:51.120
Let's keep going, alright?

33:51.200 --> 33:51.550
Sure.

33:51.590 --> 33:52.880
Candied hawthorns!

33:56.640 --> 33:57.830
Trinkets!

33:58.070 --> 33:59.090
Trinkets for sale!

33:59.090 --> 34:00.150
Fresh vegetables!

34:03.960 --> 34:05.090
Candied hawthorns!

34:16.469 --> 34:17.360
How about a flatbread?

34:17.360 --> 34:18.070
Not now.

34:18.150 --> 34:18.840
It's freshly baked.

34:18.840 --> 34:19.500
Very tasty.

34:19.670 --> 34:21.280
Sir, would you like a flatbread?

34:21.280 --> 34:22.340
Yes, I'll take one.

34:25.360 --> 34:25.800
Sir,

34:26.320 --> 34:27.070
I'll take half a kilo of lean meat.

34:27.070 --> 34:27.510
Got it!

34:29.000 --> 34:29.730
Vegetables.

34:30.590 --> 34:31.920
Fresh vegetables!

34:51.440 --> 34:52.150
Be patient.

34:53.219 --> 34:54.429
It'll be done soon.

35:31.400 --> 35:33.280
Heaven cares for every living creature.

35:33.280 --> 35:34.610
This puppy is innocent.

35:35.280 --> 35:37.410
Why must you commit a sin by killing it?

35:38.590 --> 35:40.110
You finally decided to show up

35:40.110 --> 35:41.840
after following me all the way here.

35:41.840 --> 35:42.480
What?

35:43.030 --> 35:43.800
Do you think

35:43.800 --> 35:45.600
you are a merciful living Buddha

35:45.800 --> 35:48.060
who doesn't descend until blood is seen?

35:49.760 --> 35:50.480
Besides,

35:52.960 --> 35:54.690
who said I would kill the puppy?

36:00.030 --> 36:01.630
You are the one I plan to kill.

36:07.070 --> 36:08.550
You won't be able to do so, miss.

36:08.550 --> 36:11.110
For snatching my captives away
right under my nose,

36:11.110 --> 36:12.570
you really are something.

36:12.710 --> 36:14.310
That said, I'm very curious.

36:14.410 --> 36:15.920
Hadn't you fled like a loser

36:15.920 --> 36:17.000
who lost his home?

36:17.550 --> 36:18.750
Why did you come back?

36:19.440 --> 36:20.770
Do you have a death wish?

36:23.760 --> 36:25.420
I'd like a word with you, miss.

36:25.550 --> 36:26.230
About what?

36:26.880 --> 36:28.140
About my tribulation,

36:28.440 --> 36:29.280
and my path.

36:31.070 --> 36:32.200
I'm not interested.

36:32.360 --> 36:33.160
But what if...

36:34.440 --> 36:36.590
you are my tribulation?

36:50.070 --> 36:51.630
Thank you for walking me here.

36:51.630 --> 36:52.670
You're welcome, Miss Xin.

36:52.670 --> 36:54.000
It was no trouble at all.

36:54.400 --> 36:55.230
Has the intruder

36:55.230 --> 36:56.090
been found yet?

36:56.190 --> 36:56.960
No, not yet.

36:57.400 --> 36:58.800
I can't live stay in that room anymore.

36:58.800 --> 37:00.600
There are no spare rooms
in the valley either.

37:00.600 --> 37:01.430
Luckily, Mr. Lu has

37:01.430 --> 37:02.590
a vacant guest room here.

37:02.590 --> 37:04.790
It's the perfect place for my recovery.

37:05.700 --> 37:06.630
And your luggage...

37:06.630 --> 37:07.550
Just put it here.

37:07.550 --> 37:08.000
Sure.

37:08.710 --> 37:09.310
Thank you.

37:22.000 --> 37:23.460
Have a good rest, Miss Xin.

37:25.440 --> 37:25.900
See you.

37:37.310 --> 37:39.950
[Jiujue Cave]

37:44.320 --> 37:46.840
War Demons' bodies are like half gods'

37:47.290 --> 37:48.630
with unconventional constitutions.

37:48.630 --> 37:49.590
They live long lives

37:49.590 --> 37:50.720
and never feel pain.

37:51.710 --> 37:52.920
Pain is blocked

37:52.920 --> 37:54.030
by the stone marrow

37:54.030 --> 37:55.280
in your bones.

37:56.360 --> 37:57.190
This time, to renew bones,

37:57.190 --> 37:59.280
your old bones will be shattered
after you take certain medicine.

37:59.280 --> 38:01.150
Then, they will be soaked and dissolved

38:01.150 --> 38:02.800
in Dragon Burning Sand.

38:08.110 --> 38:09.970
This is the front leg bone of a ram.

38:10.510 --> 38:11.800
It's indestructible.

38:21.960 --> 38:23.160
It's really working.

38:24.110 --> 38:25.570
The upcoming bone renewal

38:25.920 --> 38:27.400
won't be like how it was when you

38:27.400 --> 38:29.000
renewed your skin and flesh.

38:29.400 --> 38:30.670
When your bones shatter

38:30.670 --> 38:32.030
and your stone marrow vanishes,

38:32.030 --> 38:34.550
you will be struck
by sudden and severe pain.

38:36.190 --> 38:38.030
Have you ever thought about

38:38.550 --> 38:39.880
how painful it would be?

38:41.320 --> 38:42.180
Yes, of course.

38:43.000 --> 38:43.920
This is my wish.

38:50.360 --> 38:50.960
Fine then.

38:52.230 --> 38:53.150
Drink this.

38:53.710 --> 38:54.640
We'll proceed to

38:54.880 --> 38:56.540
the bone renewal in a few days.

39:11.510 --> 39:11.920
Lu,

39:12.590 --> 39:14.250
you are weak now. Walk slower.

39:18.070 --> 39:18.760
Senior,

39:19.630 --> 39:20.630
what happened to Mr. Lu?

39:20.630 --> 39:21.160
Nothing.

39:21.230 --> 39:22.550
He just caught a cold.

39:23.960 --> 39:24.760
A cold?

39:25.320 --> 39:25.920
Exactly.

39:26.150 --> 39:26.880
Just a cold.

39:27.480 --> 39:28.280
I'm fine.

39:29.110 --> 39:29.970
Leave him to me.

39:30.320 --> 39:30.760
Sure.

39:36.100 --> 39:36.700
Slowly.

41:33.400 --> 41:34.330
Are you alright?

41:34.920 --> 41:36.180
Don't drink the water.

41:36.280 --> 41:37.140
It's poisoned!

41:37.510 --> 41:38.400
Don't drink the water!

41:38.400 --> 41:39.260
It's poisoned!

41:39.550 --> 41:40.400
Don't drink the water!

41:40.400 --> 41:41.340
It's poisoned!

41:41.510 --> 41:42.510
The water is poisoned!

41:42.510 --> 41:43.480
Don't drink the water!

41:43.480 --> 41:44.340
It's poisoned!

41:44.590 --> 41:45.320
Don't drink the water!

41:45.320 --> 41:46.550
It's poisoned!

41:47.110 --> 41:47.840
I'm thirsty.

41:48.590 --> 41:49.440
Give me water.

41:50.150 --> 41:51.100
I'm thirsty.

41:53.110 --> 41:54.510
But I can't drink the water.

41:54.510 --> 41:55.370
It's poisoned.

41:56.760 --> 41:58.090
I can't drink the water!

41:59.000 --> 42:00.030
It's poisoned.

42:02.150 --> 42:02.880
I'm thirsty.

42:03.360 --> 42:04.440
I can't drink the water.

42:04.440 --> 42:05.300
It's poisoned.

42:06.110 --> 42:06.920
I'm thirsty.

42:07.880 --> 42:08.740
I'm so thirsty.

42:09.400 --> 42:10.550
But I can't drink the water.

42:10.550 --> 42:11.440
It's poisoned.

42:12.230 --> 42:12.960
I'm thirsty.

42:14.300 --> 42:15.670
But I can't drink the water.

42:15.670 --> 42:16.530
It's poisoned.

42:17.880 --> 42:19.210
I can't drink the water!

42:19.280 --> 42:20.070
I'm thirsty.

42:20.190 --> 42:21.450
The water is poisoned.

42:22.000 --> 42:23.260
The water is poisoned.

42:23.960 --> 42:25.290
I can't drink the water.

42:26.550 --> 42:27.670
It's poisoned.

42:28.230 --> 42:29.160
I can't drink it.

42:29.960 --> 42:30.550
I can't.

42:42.230 --> 42:43.690
What's with Immortal Xin?

42:46.120 --> 42:47.720
Her body can't retain water.

42:47.800 --> 42:49.030
The Fish Drinking Technique

42:49.030 --> 42:50.880
can't help her for too much longer.

42:50.880 --> 42:52.480
Is there any other solution?

42:53.630 --> 42:55.550
The only way
to break the Spell of Utterance

42:55.550 --> 42:56.710
is to kill the person who cast the spell.
